---
<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none text-gray-900 md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl dark:text-white">About me</h2>
<p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Passionate about sports, I see physical activity as a source of well-being and personal growth. My main discipline is football, which I have practiced from an early age, allowing me to develop essential values such as respect, teamwork, and resilience.</p>
<div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full">
    <hr class="w-64 h-1 my-8 bg-gray-200 border-0 rounded-sm dark:bg-gray-700">
    <div class="absolute px-4 -translate-x-1/2 bg-white left-1/2 dark:bg-gray-950">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 18 14">
            <path d="M6 0H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4v1a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H2a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h1a5.006 5.006 0 0 0 5-5V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2Zm10 0h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4v1a3 3 0 0 1-3 3h-1a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h1a5.006 5.006 0 0 0 5-5V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2Z"/>
        </svg>
    </div>
</div>
<p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 font-bold mb-10">I consider sports to be a fundamental pillar of life, not only for its health benefits but also for its ability to foster discipline, camaraderie, and strong relationships.</p>

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
    {PHOTOS.map(photo => (
        <figure class="relative max-w-sm transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer filter grayscale hover:grayscale-0 items-center">
            <div class="max-w-sm p-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out">
                <AboutItem {...photo} />
            </div>              
        </figure>
    ))}
</div>